{
  "stem": "27507.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And somebody came from below and complained that the plaster is falling on their heads because we were walking around, and the attic was probably-- it was all a bit shabby.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I looked out of the window of the attic, and there was a window which was to the main street, to [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we saw-- and then I saw rickshaws, which we taking the SS people-- the big fat SS uniform people back to their headquarters.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They obviously-- that was already after the action.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was seeing it from the fourth, fifth floor, you know, or sixth floor-- what do I know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I saw those rickshaws with those fat SS people being with opened uniforms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were obviously still-- already it was hot, and they were already-- the service was finished.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were very enjoying themselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were now being driven by their slaves back to their headquarters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then somehow, I don't remember exactly, then we of course were still not able to leave the house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everything was still closed and locked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then must have sometimes later, the blockade was finally finished, and normal the traffic, or at least people, started walking again in the street.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Jurek and Damka and me, my cousins and me, we went down, and we went back to the shop.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the shop everybody already thought-- they all thought that we were gone, because my father lost his voice.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He couldn't speak anymore, because he shouted so much, because he shouted-- he ran to the main office of Schulz and was shouting, begging that they send lorry to the umschlagplatz, because after every blockade, when they had people from the shop-- workers taken to the umschlagplatz, they would send the lorry to get them out.",
      "word_count": 56
    }
  ],
